ADD *.py /usr/local/bin/
ADD scripts /usr/local/bin/scripts
ADD tools /usr/local/bin/tools
ADD defaults /usr/local/bin/defaults
WORKDIR /usr/local/bin
ENTRYPOINT ["python3"]
